    <text>
        <body>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>St. Louis</placeName>
                <date>July 20<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1851</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Enclosed I beg to hand<lb/> you Thirty Six 75/100 dollars being the
                proceeds<lb/> collected for the Occident viz from <persName>Mr<lb/>
                    Schloss</persName> $6.00—<persName>S. Jacks</persName> 9.00—<persName>H.
                    Plahto</persName> 12.75/100.<lb/>
                <persName>H. Lichtenstein</persName> 3.00—<persName>S. J. Levy</persName>
                <hi rend="underline">new subscriber</hi> 3.00—<lb/> and my self 3.00.—in all $36.75.
                as I could<lb/> not send the exact amt. Without paying 62 ct<lb/> exchange I
                enclosed here 37.00. I am sorry<lb/> to say that I could not collect any more<lb/>
                just now.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Please send the Occident as usual to<lb/>
                <persName>Messrs H. Lichtenstein</persName>, <persName>H. H. Cohen</persName>,
                    <persName>H. Plahto</persName>, <del><persName>S.
                    Jacks</persName></del><lb/><persName> S. J. Levy</persName>. <persName>J.
                    Bush</persName> and to myself, others have<lb/> discontinued to be
                subscribers.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">With best wishes for your health and<lb/> that you may have more
                success<lb/> which you labor duly <add>?</add> in<lb/> other places<add>?</add></p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">remain Dr Sir</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">Yours very Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">A. J. Satz</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
    </text>
